        <name>Notification_Body</name>
        <isViewedAsPlainText>true</isViewedAsPlainText>
        <text>We are thrilled to welcome you as a new donor to our plasma donation center. Your decision to donate plasma is an important contribution to the health and well-being of others and we are honored to be a part of that.

As you may already know, plasma is a crucial component of many life-saving therapies and treatments, including those for people with immune deficiencies, hemophilia, and other rare conditions. Your plasma donation will be used to create these vital therapies and help save lives.

We want to assure you that your safety and comfort are our top priorities. Our experienced staff will ensure a smooth and stress-free donation process for you. We will also compensate you for your time and effort as a token of our appreciation. To schedule your first plasma donation, please click the button below.</text>
    </textTemplates>
